Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时也不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的梦想在闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双眼闭上便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 现在是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓着梦想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常也和你一起向明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想坚信着 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向着天空大声呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身处的是有趣热带的第四星界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里我们要令不断减少的海水恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人鱼村打倒了复活岛石像后的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了追寻黑球向海底出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十七话\N消失在黑暗中的龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,是那个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再张开点吧,海之塞!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好捉住了后便可以烧来吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,这不是蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,复活岛石像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,你是渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是这个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是多坏达大人的黑球!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活岛石像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把它交回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧,钢铁兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,巴哈路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于找到黑球了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且渡他们也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我立即来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但得到了黑球, 连渡他们也捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么高兴的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一起跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳得较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加快速度!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快抢回来,钢铁兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神奇饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候用鱼子饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又见面了呢,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔…魔界三兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地把黑球给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎可以交给你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无用的反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗黑魔神黑龙角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已正在来这第四星界的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要这个的话便试试抢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟妹们,追!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我们趁这时候把海之塞塞回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,但到底要怎样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是干鱼婆婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干鱼婆婆?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,你想干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要想被卷进事件里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩我上次已报了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么激动啊,拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里的话可以放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你真的激怒我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣,那来拼拼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三百年来守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个海之塞的干鱼婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗,把地图流放出来的便是婆婆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是渡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要尽快把海之塞塞好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果所有的海水也流走了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋便不会再恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干鱼婆婆,我们应怎样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,是那个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那复活岛石像手上的开关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭向左面的话水便会停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再继续扭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前流走了的水便会升回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!我明白了,婆婆!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以被你这样做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙上一次应该已打倒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多路飞龙只要剩下头部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要复活多少次也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去,去,去!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去,去,去!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吃这一招吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭飞龙拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的,没用的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被它捉住一次后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不论怎样也不会再放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有没有电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话?没有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拾到这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上,弟妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼,能好好玩一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身手不错呢,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了,弟妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界暗黑光线!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的攻击只是擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要替我挡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能够保护这家伙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子…男人有非做不可的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说,现在正是这时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?海火子,做得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还未死吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟妹们,追!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了,拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺命一击!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,要你等对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部魔神由在下缠着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁这时候把海之塞关掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,就由你开始收拾吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀,被电麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是多坏达向海之塞下的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果是真正的勇者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该…应该可以做得到的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,这样连接近也做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说泄气话,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论遇上什么事也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,超了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续扭令海水恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟把海之塞关了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好收拾你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小儿科
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼跑哪了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢轻看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑龙角很快便到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑球之后再取吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼,一群蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是顽强的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空幻龙波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶,掉到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着只剩下把海水复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到以前从未有过的邪恶之气在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是暗黑魔神黑龙角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这便是黑龙角?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗…暗黑魔神?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来制裁你!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这一招吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥,有部奇怪的魔神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他一起解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑球!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会把它给你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼豪拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙雷拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把力量聚集起来战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦,这家伙不由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由我解决不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,不要勉强啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大的黑暗力量黑球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变成为我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好看看黑球的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是邪恶的力量聚集而成的暗黑空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的葬身之地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:20:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢进去暗黑空间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出尽全力吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论遇到什么事也不可以放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才这样说的,不是龙神丸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错,你要一直记紧这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,星界山拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…龙神丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们魔界三兄弟胜利了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…龙神丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?这个胸口在驱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! 已不能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也一个劲儿地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油门不用放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直踏着 Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是速度的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TONIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直望着的瞳孔涌上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜 MY LOVE

